        <p>This document describes the structure and function of the Department of Happiness, Inc. (hereafter <acronym title="Department of Happiness">DoH</acronym>) as required for completion of <acronym title="Internal Revenue Service">IRS</acronym> form 1023: Application for Recognition of Exemption Under Section 501(c)(3) of the Internal Revenue Code.</p>
