        <h2>Purpose</h2>

        <p>The <acronym title="Department of Happiness">DoH</acronym> is an open-source software management firm responsible for the execution of a two-year series of software releases aimed at replacing the world economy. The software releases are timed with the script to the videoblog <a href="http://technoanarchy.wikia.com"><cite>Technoanarchist Revolution</cite></a>.</p>

